		"description": {
			"value": "<p><span><strong>Bonus Action</strong> </span>- 1 Creature (60 ft.) - 1 Round - Magical</p><p>When you have an &amp;reference[illusoryimages]{illusory image} of 1st level or higher active, you can make it blast and hinder a creature.</p><p><strong>Ranged Spell Attack</strong> </p><p>A creature within the illusion's area or within 5 ft. of the illusion imposes disadvantage on this attack roll.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Force damage equal to 1d6 per level of the spell that created the illusory image. Target's speed is halved.</p></li></ul><p></p><p>If the spell creating the illusory image ends, the target's speed is no longer halved.</p>",
